Description: sparse-ir - A library for the intermediate representation of propagators
 This library provides routines for constructing and working with the intermediate 
 representation of correlation functions. It provides:
 on-the-fly computation of basis functions for arbitrary cutoff Î›
 basis functions and singular values are accurate to full precision
 routines for sparse sampling
